艾米·舒默在对她外表的评论中分享了库欣综合症的诊断https://www.nme.com/news/tv/amy-schumer-shares-cushings-syndrome-diagnosis-amid-comments-about-her-appearance-3592274?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=amy-schumer-shares-关于她外表的评论中的库欣综合症诊断Tom SkinnerSat, 24 Feb 2024 14:53:48 +0000 Film NewsTV News https://www.nme.com/?p=3592274 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/AmySchumer-news.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="艾米·舒默" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/AmySchumer-news.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/AmySchumer-news-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/AmySchumer-news-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/AmySchumer-news-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/AmySchumer-news-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/AmySchumer-news-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “这就是我意识到出问题的方式 [...] 互联网是不败的”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/amy-schumer-shares-cushings-syndrome-diagnosis-amid-comments-about-her-appearance-3592274">艾米·舒默 (Amy Schumer) 在有关她外表的评论中分享了库欣综合症的诊断结果，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/AmySchumer-news.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="艾米·舒默" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/AmySchumer-news.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/AmySchumer-news-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/AmySchumer-news-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/AmySchumer-news-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/AmySchumer-news-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/AmySchumer-news-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>艾米·舒默分享说，她已被诊断出患有库欣综合症。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.nhs.uk/conditions/cushings-syndrome/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">英国国家医疗服务体系 (NHS)</a>称，这种罕见的病症是由于体内皮质醇（主要应激激素）过多引起的，如果不及时治疗可能会导致严重后果。症状可能包括体重增加和脸色发红、浮肿、圆圆。</p><p>昨天（2 月 23 日星期五），42 岁的喜剧演员兼演员舒默在记者杰西卡·耶林的<a href="https://newsnotnoisejessicayellin.substack.com/p/the-news-not-noise-letter-amy-schumer" target="_blank" rel="noopener">“新闻不是噪音”</a>时事通讯中证实了她的诊断结果。</p><p>这一更新是在粉丝们开始询问为什么她在最近接受关于她的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/hulu">Hulu</a>喜剧剧集《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/david-byrne-stars-as-amy-schumers-doctor-in-new-trailer-for-life-beth-3157698"><em>生活与贝丝》</em></a>第二季的采访时显得有一张“浮肿”的脸之后发布的。</p><p>本月早些时候，舒默<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/C3YaFBrO8HI/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link&amp;igsh=MzRlODBiNWFlZA%3D%3D" target="_blank" rel="noopener">回应</a>了“每个人对她的脸的看法”，她说：“我的世界里现在发生了一些医学和荷尔蒙问题，但我没事。”</p><p>耶林在她最新的时事通讯中证实：“在仇恨者来找艾米之后，我联系了她。她说她患有外源性库欣综合征，是因注射高剂量类固醇而引起的。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C3YaFBrO8HI/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="disp